    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-barnes-hard-problem-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes several security challenges involved with the increasingly common practice of third-party hosting of applications, in particular the inability to know with a high level of assurance that the hosting provider is authorized to offer an application on behalf of an organization or individual.</description>
